Day 2 project Todo App with LocalStorage hi hai.

Is project ka roadmap:

📝 Features

Add Task → Input field se task add hoga.

Show Tasks → Saare tasks ek list mein appear honge.

Mark as Complete → Checkbox ya line-through style se.

Delete Task → Har task ke sath ❌ button.

Save in LocalStorage → Refresh ke baad bhi tasks wahan rahen.

⚡ Extra Challenge

"Clear All Tasks" button add karo.

Completed tasks ko alag style do (for example green background).

Tasks ko date & time ke sath save karo